    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "9VrOC",
      "x": -7420,
      "y": 15,
      "name": "animNote",
      "width": 520,
      "height": 480,
      "content": "🎬 TAB CYCLING ANIMATION — home-light hero\n\n⏱ Interval: every 3 seconds, advance to next tab (loop)\nOrder: Dashboard → Candidates → Tests → Talent Pool → Dashboard…\n\n📐 Tab states (tabsRow · nBoWf)\nActive tab:\n  • Bottom border: 2px solid #2563EB\n  • Icon fill: #2563EB\n  • Label fill: #2563EB · fontWeight 600\nInactive tab:\n  • No bottom border\n  • Icon fill: #94A3B8\n  • Label fill: #64748B · fontWeight normal\n\n🖼 Dashboard mock swap (v5-dashboard-mock · O028t)\nOn tab change, cross-fade the mock to the matching component:\n  Dashboard   → ref: Ttv4P\n  Candidates  → ref: aAxfF\n  Tests       → ref: XR1Sc\n  Talent Pool → ref: 3riNp\n\n✨ Transition spec\n  • Duration: 400ms\n  • Easing: ease-in-out\n  • Effect: opacity 1→0 (outgoing) / 0→1 (incoming)\n    + translateY: 0px→8px (out) / -8px→0px (in)\n  • Overlap: both run simultaneously (cross-fade)\n\n📌 Implementation note (Next.js)\n  useState(activeTab), useEffect with setInterval(3000)\n  Tailwind: transition-opacity duration-400 + translate-y\n  Swap <component> inside the mock frame using conditional render"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "PnIOZ",
      "x": -7420,
      "y": -18,
      "name": "sTitle",
      "fill": "#ffffffff",
      "content": "Tab Animation — 4 UI States (cycles every 3s)",
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontWeight": "700"
    },
