    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "Dga1b",
      "x": -7420,
      "y": 861,
      "name": "homeVariantsNote",
      "width": 520,
      "height": 320,
      "content": "🏠 TWO HOME PAGE VARIANTS\n\nTwo homepage designs exist — one will be chosen during Phase 3:\n• home-dark — dark hero (brand-navy bg, gradient overlay)\n• home-light — light hero (white bg, tab-cycling animation in hero)\n\nThe state frames (state-1-dashboard, state-2-candidates, state-3-tests, state-4-talent-pool) are the mock dashboard images swapped in the home-light hero animation. See animNote above for full spec.\n\n📌 Decision point: pick ONE variant before Phase 3 implementation begins. The other can be archived."
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "G2Bab",
      "x": -7420,
      "y": 1276,
      "name": "missingFramesNote",
      "width": 520,
      "height": 431,
      "content": "⚠️ MISSING FRAMES — REQUIRED BEFORE PHASE 3\n\nThese frames still need to be designed:\n• for-candidates — /for-candidates landing page\n  (CrismaScore gauge visual, share examples, social proof, CTA)\n• for-companies — /for-companies landing page\n  (B2B hero, feature cards, trust bar, dual CTAs)\n• pricing — /pricing\n  (4-plan cards, billing toggle, Pro card taller + 'Most Popular')\n• contact — /contact\n  (demo request form, fields, consent checkbox, success toast)\n• nav-mobile — hamburger sheet open state at 375px\n• nav-shell — NavShell reusable component (mark reusable: true)\n  (required by auth.pen + test-flow.pen as import reference)\n\nPhase 3 cannot begin until all 6 are complete."
    }
  ]
}